## Microsoft Sentinel

### Send Incydr Alerts to Sentinel with py42 and the Azure Monitor data collector API

Microsoft Sentinel can ingest arbitrary json data through the [data collector API](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-monitor/logs/data-collector-api),
which accepts json records over HTTP.

This guide will outline how to send Incydr Alerts to Sentinel with a Python script using [py42](https://py42docs.code42.com)
and the data collector API. While this example will focus on Incydr Alerts, the following pattern can be re-used for any
type of data you can pull from the Code42 API.

